    "Firstly, EEMD is employed for decomposing PV power data into different sets of frequency ranges.",
    "The decomposed components are classified into three main categories, high-frequency, and intermediate-frequency.",
    "These three categories are separately forecasted using a parameters-weight integration model and summed to get the actual PV signal.",
    "Experimental results show that an individual forecast strategy provides better precision than a direct forecasting method.",
    "Zhou et al."
